%% Data Flow Diagram for caikit-nlp
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
%% Source: architecture/rhoai-2.24/caikit-nlp.md

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client
    participant ServingLayer as Model Serving Layer<br/>(ModelMesh / KServe)
    participant HTTP as Caikit HTTP Server<br/>8080/TCP
    participant gRPC as Caikit gRPC Server<br/>8085/TCP
    participant LocalModule as Local Module<br/>(TextGen / Embedding)
    participant TGISClient as TGISGenerationClient
    participant TGIS as TGIS Server<br/>8033-8034/TCP gRPC
    participant HFModel as HuggingFace Model<br/>(local)
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,HFHub: Flow 1: Local Text Generation (Fine-tuned/Prompt-tuned)
    Client->>ServingLayer: Inference Request
    ServingLayer->>HTTP: POST /api/v1/task/text-generation<br/>8080/TCP HTTP, Optional TLS
    HTTP->>LocalModule: Route to TextGeneration/<br/>PeftPromptTuning module
    LocalModule->>HFModel: Load & run model<br/>(in-process)
    HFModel-->>LocalModule: Generated text
    LocalModule-->>HTTP: Response
    HTTP-->>ServingLayer: JSON Response
    ServingLayer-->>Client: Inference Response

    Note over Client,HFHub: Flow 2: Remote Text Generation via TGIS
    Client->>ServingLayer: Inference Request
    ServingLayer->>gRPC: TextGenerationTask RPC<br/>8085/TCP gRPC, Optional mTLS
    gRPC->>TGISClient: Route to TextGenerationTGIS/<br/>PeftPromptTuningTGIS module
    TGISClient->>TGIS: gRPC GenerateText<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS
    TGIS-->>TGISClient: Generated text
    TGISClient-->>gRPC: Response
    gRPC-->>ServingLayer: gRPC Response
    ServingLayer-->>Client: Inference Response

    Note over Client,HFHub: Flow 3: Text Embedding
    Client->>ServingLayer: Embedding Request
    ServingLayer->>HTTP: POST /api/v1/task/embedding<br/>8080/TCP HTTP, Optional TLS
    HTTP->>LocalModule: Route to EmbeddingModule
    LocalModule->>HFModel: SentenceTransformer encode<br/>(in-process)
    HFModel-->>LocalModule: Embedding vectors
    LocalModule-->>HTTP: Response
    HTTP-->>ServingLayer: JSON Response
    ServingLayer-->>Client: Embedding Response

    Note over Client,HFHub: Flow 4: Gateway Mode (REST + gRPC)
    Client->>HTTP: POST /api/v1/task/*<br/>8080/TCP HTTP, Optional TLS
    HTTP->>gRPC: Forward to gRPC backend<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    gRPC->>TGISClient: Route to TGIS module
    TGISClient->>TGIS: gRPC inference<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS
    TGIS-->>TGISClient: Result
    TGISClient-->>gRPC: Response
    gRPC-->>HTTP: gRPC Response
    HTTP-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client,HFHub: Model Download (startup, when ALLOW_DOWNLOADS=1)
    LocalModule->>HFHub: Download model artifacts<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, TLS 1.2+<br/>Token auth (optional)
    HFHub-->>LocalModule: Model files
